w.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kat-graham-diana-ross@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kat-graham-diana-ross@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/kat-graham-diana-ross@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>即将上映的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-jackson">迈克尔·杰克逊</a>传记片<em>《迈克尔》</em>宣布了新的演员阵容。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/michael-jackson-biopic-cast-whos-who-3590015">这是迈克尔·杰克逊传记片中的扮演者</a></strong></li></ul><p><em>迈克尔</em>新选的角色包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/diana-ross">戴安娜·罗斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/quincy-jones">昆西·琼斯</a>和流行音乐之王的姐姐拉·托亚·杰克逊等传奇人物。据<a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/news/michael-jackson-biopic-kat-graham-diana-ross-larenz-tate-berry-gordy-1235951141/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a>报道， <em>《吸血鬼日记》</em>明星凯特·格雷厄姆将饰演标志性的戴安娜·罗斯。</p><p>格雷厄姆在社交媒体上谈到她的选角时写道：“很高兴能扮演传奇人物戴安娜·罗斯……由伟大的安东尼·福卡执导。我迫不及待地想让大家看到这部电影和其中精彩的表演。感谢 Graham King、Vickie Thomas 和 Fuqua 先生让我有幸支持重述我们音乐史上的这一关键时代。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C48eu3Os-HD/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4p